---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="天 ROCK FEST 2026 The Summer Camp | 輪廻タヲ"
  description="天 ROCK FEST 2026 The Summer Camp DAY1 出演情報。"
  ogImage="/tenrock-2026-live-cover.webp"
  noindex={true}
>
  <div class="pt-24 pb-16 px-5 md:px-8 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">

      <div class="py-12 mb-8">
        <h1 class="font-mincho text-text-primary text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light tracking-[0.1em] leading-relaxed">
          【天 ROCK FEST 2026<br />The Summer Camp】
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-video overflow-hidden bg-[#1e1c18] rounded-sm mb-10">
        <img src="/tenrock-2026-live-cover.webp" alt="天 ROCK FEST 2026 The Summer Camp 輪廻タヲ" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>

      <div class="text-text-muted text-[15px] font-light leading-[2] space-y-6">
        <p>
          【DAY 1】2026/7/25（土）<br />
          RED TENT　21:10～<br />
          輪廻タヲ
        </p>

        <p>
          ↓ライブ会場URL。<br />
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@1069summer" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-2 decoration-text-faint/40 text-text-primary hover:text-text-primary/80 transition-colors duration-300">https://www.youtube.com/@1069summer</a>
        </p>

        <p>
          当日、ご来場予定の皆様は、お時間（21:10～）、会場（RED TENT）をお間違えのないよう、ご注意ください。
        </p>

        <div class="pt-4 space-y-2 text-[13px]">
          <p><a href="https://tenrocksummer2026.netlify.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-2 decoration-text-faint/40 text-text-muted hover:text-text-primary transition-colors duration-300">天 ROCK FEST 2026 公式サイト</a></p>
          <p><a href="/blog/tenrock-fest-2026-guide" class="underline underline-offset-2 decoration-text-faint/40 text-text-muted hover:text-text-primary transition-colors duration-300">過去記事：AI音楽ロックフェス「天ROCK FEST 2026」（7/24-26）。輪廻タヲの最後のお願い。</a></p>
          <p><a href="/news/tenrock-2026" class="underline underline-offset-2 decoration-text-faint/40 text-text-muted hover:text-text-primary transition-colors duration-300">出演のお知らせ</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
